levels.helpHTML:
The version pairs are s6/s6j and peyg/peygj; the medalless level is bp.

The level groupings are mostly obvious; the movement group is intended to be hover-based/fluddless movement levels, and was defined in Nov 2020 as:

b3 b3s b4 b6 b6s r1 r2 r3 r4 r4s r5
g1s p2 p2s p3 p6s s2 s2s s3 s4 s4s
n1 n2 n6 n6s q3 q4 q6 c
